        <abstract>
            The dataset provides 153 vegetation relevés (4889 associated occurrences) collected in 2021, as well as 99 vegetation relevés (3309 associated occurrences) collected in 2022. The previous vegetation data sampled in 2019-2020 available through GBIF, DOI10.15468/y2yuq8. See DOI: 10.3897/BDJ.9.e71266 for background and details of sampling methods.
        </abstract>
